headline: Estée Lauder Names Nia Long as Brand Ambassador for North America
summary: NEW YORK, October 09, 2025--Estée Lauder today announced award-winning actor, producer and author Nia Long as its first Brand Ambassador exclusive to North America. In this role, Nia will appear in campaigns across digital, TV, and print for the brand’s skincare and makeup franchises.

headline: Can Estée Lauder (EL) Leverage Its India Innovation Push to Reinforce Long-Term Brand Leadership?
summary: Earlier this week, The Estée Lauder Companies Inc. announced the winners of BEAUTY&YOU India 2025, a program in partnership with Startup India and Nykaa, aimed at supporting India’s next generation of beauty entrepreneurs through funding, mentorship, and business platforms. This year’s program introduced the BEAUTY&YOU Visionary Women’s Award, highlighting Estée Lauder’s commitment to driving innovation and empowering women entrepreneurs in emerging markets. headline: Helen of Troy (HELE) Tops Q2 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Helen of Troy (HELE) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +9.26% and +3.09%, respectively, for the quarter ended August 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
